children.subject: The CS70 Piazza for Spring has been set up, so I think you might want to join that Piazza group and try posting there to see if any instructors might be able to give you a more concrete answer for potential midterm dates this upcoming semester.

history.content:
Go on archive.org and find an older version of the website and just go through the weeks. http://web.archive.org/web/20180506171655/http://www.eecs70.org/ (this is for 2018)

"Midterm 1 is on Tuesday, February 13 from 7-9 pm. Midterm 2 is on Monday, March 19 from 7-9 pm. Final is on Thursday, May 10 from 3-6 pm. Exams conflict? We will release a form for you to fill out on Piazza."
